Chadrick Evan FULKS, petitioner,

UNITED STATES. No. 12-8364. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 683 F.3d 512 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
